name: 2014 Core Set Booster Battle Pack

extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
Experience the fun of a two-player pack war. GRab a friend, bust open a booster, and begin battling!
Each Booster Battle Pack contains:
• Two 22-card semi-randomized decks
• Two 15-card Magic 2014 booster packs
• Magic "learn to play" guide
• Rules insert

extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
With your horde of warriors, shamans, and wild beasts, your goal is to put your opponents on the back foot, then smash through their defenses. This deck lets you take the offensive, dominating the battle and denying your enemy time to execute a strategy.

Each event deck contains a preconstructed 60-card deck, 10 rares, and a 15-card sideboard.
